# Requirements 

# High-level requirements
These are the features of my project
1.Create new account
2.Update information of existing account
3.For transactions
4.Check the details of exixting account
5.Removing existing account
6.View customer's list
7.Exit

# Low-level requirements
Functions used 
1.menu()      //  displays the welcome screen to perform different banking activities
2.new_acc()   //  creates a new customer account
3.view list() //  view the customerâ€™s banking information 
4.edit()      //  used for changing the address and phone number of a particular customer account
5.transact() //   deposit and withdraw money to and from a particular customer account
6.erase()    //   for deleting a customer account
7.see()      //   shows account and personal details of the customer
